rows.label: fev04_130_125_msg0002
rows.name:
It's such a relief to
be back on solid ground!

rows.label: fev04_130_125_msg0003
rows.name:
That was quite
a long voyage, wasn't it...

rows.label: fev04_130_125_msg0004
rows.name:
I'm surprised by how
deserted this place is.

rows.label: fev04_130_125_msg0005
rows.name:
Perhaps it's because this port is
situated some distance from the city.

rows.label: fev04_130_125_msg0006
rows.name:
You're probably right.
Our next step is to make
our way to the imperial capital.

rows.label: fev04_130_125_msg0007
rows.name:
From what they told me on the ship, we
just need to exit the port on the right
and it's a straight path from there.

rows.label: fev04_130_125_msg0008
rows.name:
It seems close, but it's unfamiliar
territory, so we need to
proceed carefully.

rows.label: fev04_130_125_msg0009
rows.name:
Right.
Let's head out once we're prepared.
